<view class="page bubble-page paper-page">
  <view class="page-head floral-title-box bubble-head">
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-left corner-ornament--blue"></view>
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-right corner-ornament--gold"></view>
    <text class="seal-flower">废话标本室</text>
    <text class="hero-title">吗喽的泡泡机</text>
    <text class="subtext">有些话听起来很大，其实只是空气很多。把职场废话放进泡泡里，会比较容易看清它。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="note-card bubble-note paper-edge">
    <view class="paper-corner right"></view>
    <text>泡泡机只做本地随机展示，不联网、不识别真实聊天，也不替你做决定。</text>
    <view class="bubble-tags">
      <text>模糊评价</text>
      <text>甩锅</text>
      <text>KPI 压迫</text>
      <text>情绪拉扯</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <character-card image="{{companion.image}}" name="{{companion.name}}" tag="{{companion.tag}}" message="{{companion.message}}" sub-message="{{companion.subMessage}}" variant="{{companion.variant}}" size="{{companion.size}}" />

  <view class="ornament-card bubble-lab">
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-left corner-ornament--blue"></view>
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-right corner-ornament--gold"></view>
    <text class="paper-seal">今日废话标本</text>
    <view class="main-bubble {{popped ? 'is-popped' : ''}}">
      <view class="tiny-bubble b1"></view>
      <view class="tiny-bubble b2"></view>
      <view class="tiny-bubble b3"></view>
      <block wx:if="{{bubble}}">
        <text class="bubble-category">{{bubble.category}}</text>
        <text class="bubble-text">{{bubble.text}}</text>
      </block>
      <block wx:else>
        <text class="bubble-category">待识别</text>
        <text class="bubble-text empty-bubble-text">按一下按钮，让一颗职场废话浮上来。</text>
      </block>
    </view>
    <button wx:if="{{bubble && !popped}}" class="sticker-button secondary pop-button" bindtap="popLdBubble">戳破这句废话</button>
    <button wx:if="{{!bubble}}" class="sticker-button pop-button" bindtap="drawBubble">摇一颗泡泡</button>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{popped}}" class="archive-card result-card paper-edge">
    <view class="paper-corner bottom-right"></view>
    <text class="paper-seal result-seal">拆解说明纸</text>
    <text class="result-line strong">已识别职场废话，建议不要内化。</text>
    <text class="result-line">你可以把它当成一句{{bubble.category}}，而不是事实。</text>
    <text class="result-line">泡泡已破。它没有你想象中那么坚固。</text>
    <view class="action-row">
      <button class="sticker-button" bindtap="drawBubble">再来一个</button>
      <button class="sticker-button green" bindtap="goDiary">记进日记</button>
      <button class="sticker-button secondary" bindtap="acknowledge">我知道了</button>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>